<body class="splash">
  <header class="main">
    <section class="mobile_admin_nav">
      <%= link_to 'OpenGovernment', root_path, class: 'logo' %>
    </section>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <%= link_to 'OpenGovernment', root_path, class: 'logo' %>
      <div class="news_signup" id="news_signup">
        <div class="leftCol">
          <h1>The "We The People" for every elected official.</h1>
          <p>Get notified and ask a question when we launch</p>
          <nav>
            <ul class="level">
              <li class="active" data-type="individual">
                <a href="#">Individual</a>
                <i class="icon-angle-down"></i>
              </li>
              <li data-type="elected_official">
                <a href="#">Elected Official</a>
                <i class="icon-angle-down"></i>
              </li>
              <li data-type="organization">
                <a href="#">Organization</a>
                <i class="icon-angle-down"></i>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
          <form action="/ma/questions" class='splash-form'>
            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="E-mail">
            <input type="text" name="zipcode" id="zipcode" placeholder="Zipcode (optional)">
            <input type="hidden" name="notify_type" id="notify_type" value="individual">
            <input type="submit" value="Notify Me" class="cta-pill">
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="rightCol">
          <p>Not just for Presidents anymore. Ask and vote on questions for over 100,000 elected officials. Also, question and petition any verified Twitter account.</p><br> 
		  <p>Sign up now to be the first to submit a question when we launch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </header>
  <nav class="scroll_content below">
    <a href="/splash#content_body" class="show_below">How It Works</a>
  </nav>
  <nav class="scroll_content above" style="display:none;">
    <a href="/splash#" class="show_above">Get Notified</a>
  </nav>
